narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I was able to learn more about Korean grammar and language through the course.
I improved my Korean ability in writing, speaking and listening.
Learned a lot of new vocabulary, and practiced our speaking skills through presentations and conversation during class.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I really enjoyed the course and it was engaging and interactive with both the teachers and fellow classmates.

Love the teacher (  is awesome) and she is definitely a strength of the class - always very enthusiastic about class and teaching us. Weakness is that we didn't really get any grades back so even now I as I am evaluating this class I am not sure what grade I will get.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I would absolutely recommend this course to another student who wishes to deepen their knowledge of Korean grammar and language.
Yes I would definitely recommend this course! Great way to continue learning and practicing Korean in a chill environment.
